/>\n<br />\n世界工廠方面<br />\n世界工人以後就唔可以捱辛苦加班, 因為抵抗力會下降, 吸引病毒復發<br />\n工人太密雜, 宿舍太迫又要引爆疫情<br />\n<br />\n中國旅客不能再威脅外國<br />\n因為旅客會有病毒"},{"pid":"a5cf6907a55ed98c5914a9afc760b44c51b52e96","tid":1890500,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T09:10:49.000Z","msg":"Made in China 產品會不會帶有WARS病毒粒子"},{"pid":"ff9264a120ff9fe4e03ec640dda8ccfc6981dc3f","tid":1890500,"uid":19609,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4fb1929c490661b918daeafb24d3b5cbbcfb259c","tid":1890500,"uid":3020,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T08:34:01.000Z","msg":"話會殺造精細胞tim"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T09:12:52.000Z","msg":"根本係中共想降低貧窮人口製造出黎<br />\n本身只係打算係農村地方用<br />\n<br />\n未有效控制散播能力就流左出街"},{"pid":"60023a7f502538e853fe2f267ea507f30e1ecd93","tid":1890500,"uid":63697,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T09:36:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d523f23998323051dd47e92044794dbf88719616","tid":1890500,"uid":132128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T09:37:32.000Z","msg":"個肺花左，醫返都冇撚用"},{"pid":"831b329b99ed196ddbf3aa9e43eddbecee7e8d03","tid":1890500,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T09:38:20.000Z","msg":"請問你係點得出依個結論？"},{"pid":"421d5b59042df39d233ca232ce011e2a6060e216","tid":1890500,"uid":68746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T09:40:03.000Z","msg":"之前話隻wars對亞洲人特別有攻擊力<br />\n好似係日本人最易奶嘢<br />\n唔通..."},{"pid":"af87f3346ddc0dcc78d408c86e6022856c699bec","tid":1890500,"uid":274772,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T09:41:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">共產黨真係智障，發明呢隻病毒，最終只會殺埋自己<br />\n<br />\n發明喪屍病毒嘛，起碼喪屍有樣睇<br />\n<br />\n發明呢隻，根本無得分辨，小學雞最後都一樣會中招<br />\n<br />\n小學雞咁撚蠢　　智商都唔知有無８０</span>"},{"pid":"74a35617f329333ddb39a2c7ba913a03429f4e10","tid":1890500,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-